name: There's A Monster In The Fridge
description:
There's a monster in the fridge. In the kitchen,
I told everybody, that there's a monster in the fridge. I saw it a couple times..
But nobody believes me.
I have no choice. 
Tomorrow, after everybody leaves the house, I'm going to open the gas on the stove, and put  a candle on the kitchen table.
I'll kill it, and Mom and Dad are gonna be proud of me.
